zen arbalest with arms of gleaming steel shooting quarrels with mighty power for those brave enough to risk betrayal.</i><table border="1"><tr><th>Value</th><th>Depth</th><th>Rarity</th><th>Damage Dice</th><th>To Hit</th><th>Damage</th><th>AC</th></tr><tr><td>35,000</td><td>60</td><td>20</td><td></td><td>+18</td><td>+18</td><td></td></tr></table><ul><li>Aggravates nearby creatures<li>Confers resistance to lightning<li>Confers resistance to blindness, light and dark<li>Increases strength and constitution by 2<li>Increases the damage multiplier for missiles by 2</ul><p><b>The Long Bow &#39;Belthronding&#39;</b><p><i>The great bow of Beleg Cuthalion, made of black yew and strung with elven hair that faintly shimmers a pale clear gold.</i><table border="1"><tr><th>Value</th><th>Depth</th><th>Rarity</th><th>Damage Dice</th><th>To Hit</th><th>Damage</th><th>AC</th></tr><tr><td>35,000</td><td>40</td><td>20</td><td></td><td>+20</td><td>+22</td><td></td></tr></table><ul><li>Confers resistance to disenchantment<li>Increases dexterity by 1<li>Increases speed; allows 1 more shot to be fired each combat turn; improves stealth by 1</ul><p><b>The Light Crossbow &#39;Cubragol&#39;</b><p><i>A crossbow that grants fiery speed to he who finds it, and from which shoot bolts that blaze with flame unquenchable.</i><table border="1"><tr><th>Value</th><th>Depth</th><th>Rarity</th><th>Damage Dice</th><th>To Hit</th><th>Damage</th><th>AC</th></tr><tr><td>50,000</td><td>50</td><td>25</td><td></td><td>+10</td><td>+14</td><td></td></tr></table><ul><li>Confers resistance to fire<li>Increases speed by 10</ul></div></div>

